            "title": "剎車失靈貨櫃車衝出馬路  拖頭90°懸掛半空｜有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/86258a8db064281dbde68aad05e6496a/2025-03/Clipboard17_6.png\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/d0353e6b049671f0bfd397c6360c0102/93e36303fd17414aa8c762025c0d385d-4a558df9e8eb1a83a83649a20efc6758-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67db6a8bc3de9\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67db6a8bc3deb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"剎車失靈貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90度懸掛半空消防驚險救人。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/72d072f5ac5c71f99d5f05d9d4064cdd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250319/_2025031916040762111.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">剎車失靈貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90度懸掛半空消防驚險救人。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>在陝西，一條高速公路有貨櫃車衝上避險車道，拖頭半掛高空，司機被困情況危急。山陽縣消防大隊城關消防救援站一車7人出動協助高速交警現場救援，成功將劉姓司機平安救出。\n\n</p><h2>拖頭與車身僅三個螺絲連接</h2>\n<p>司機劉師傅3月18日回憶，事發路段需要連續下坡，行駛過程中發現自己的剎車失靈了，唯一的辦法只有衝向前方的避險車道，劉師傅一直把住軚盤往避險車道走，『砰砰砰』，車一直在『跳』，最後車頭衝了出去，就像身處懸崖一樣。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90°懸掛半空。陝西消防\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/22b62420977c794f7825a119f84065d9/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-19-15h32m17s188.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90°懸掛半空。陝西消防\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"剎車失靈貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90°懸掛半空。陝西消防\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5a1a7c3edcea7bb2e1ed29f8d8c44f63/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-19-15h34m06s967.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        剎車失靈貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90°懸掛半空。陝西消防\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"剎車失靈貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90°懸掛半空，司機受困，如身處懸崖。 陝西消防\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fd0a852aafb60676f55ea9e652ff72d0/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-19-15h34m37s903.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        剎車失靈貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90°懸掛半空，司機受困，如身處懸崖。 陝西消防\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"剎車失靈貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90°懸掛半空，司機受困，如身處懸崖。 陝西消防\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e52604dd38e4315c6a5f23c031587778/2025-03/vlcsnap-