a-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90°懸掛半空，消防驚險救人。陝西消防\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c2bb12e07f739d26442d8e706c3e139d/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-19-15h32m26s783.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90°懸掛半空，消防驚險救人。陝西消防\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90°懸掛半空，消防驚險救人。陝西消防\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6d9af93f90aab5566e416d5b45f28355/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-19-15h32m21s721.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貨櫃車衝出公路，拖頭90°懸掛半空，消防驚險救人。陝西消防\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>司機：執翻條命</h2>\n<p>山陽縣消防大隊城關消防救援站一車7人接報後出動，協助高速交警現場救援。最終，司機劉師傅被平安救出，他感慨自己撿回了一條命。\n\n</p>\n<p>城關消防救援站指揮員說：「（事發地落差）大概有20到30米左右，車身這跟車頭相當於90°的變形，車頭跟車廂連接點只有三個螺絲。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
